description:
Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of New York, the second episode in this year's Berkshires saga. Once again no one wants to sleep near Dorinda's dead fish. The women visit a Morgan estate where Sonja spirals. Bethenny and Babs also arrive as the debauchery begins.
